OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An Indian actor has been arrested for  
OL,6, tweeting against one of the judges     
OL,7, hearing pleas against a ban on Muslim  
OL,8, girls wearing hijabs in schools.       
OL,10,FChetan Kumar was arrested in the       
OL,11,Fsouthern state of Karnataka after he   
OL,12,Fcriticised Justice Krishna Dixit.      
OL,14,FThe actor wondered why a judge, who has
OL,15,Fmade "disturbing comments" in the past,
OL,16,Fwas hearing the contentious matter.    
OL,18,FHe was referring to a 2020 order in    
OL,19,Fwhich the judge had questioned the     
OL,20,Fbehaviour of a woman who alleged rape. 
